title: Wichita Open
text:
The Wichita Open is a <a href="golf">golf</a> tournament on the <a href="Korn%20Ferry%20Tour">Korn Ferry Tour</a>. Formerly known as the Air Capital Classic, it is played annually at the Crestview Country Club in <a href="Wichita%2C%20Kansas">Wichita, Kansas</a>, U.S. It is one of four original Tour events still played.
Winners.
Bolded golfers graduated to the PGA Tour via the Korn Ferry Tour regular-season money list.
